  • Constructor Details

    • Builder

      public Builder(String accessToken)
      Create a new GetUsersSavedEpisodesRequest.Builder instance.

      The user-library-read scope must have been authorized by the user. Additionally, if the user has also authorized the user-read-playback-position scope, ResumePoint gets set.

      Parameters:
      accessToken - Required. A valid access token from the Spotify Accounts service.
      See Also:
      • Spotify: Scopes
